John S. KAMINSKI
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided November 7, 2018

John S. Kaminski, self-represented, in support of the petition.

D'AURIA, J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.

*693The petitioner John S. Kaminski's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 181 Conn. App. 903, 183 A.3d 1239 (2018), is denied.
